<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6 bg-light">
      <h4 class="my-3">こちらは増田歯科のWEB問診ページです</h4>
     

      <%= form_with model:@answer, local:true do |f| %>
        <div class="question">
          Q1.BUMP OF CHICKENで一番好きな曲はなんですか？
        </div>
          <div class="target col-md-5 col-sm-3 border border-success rounded-pill m-2 bg-color q1"><label><%= f.radio_button :q1, "q1_1", name:"q1" %>記念撮影</label></div>
          <div class="target col-md-5 col-sm-3 border border-success rounded-pill m-2 bg-color q1"><label><%= f.radio_button :q1, "q1_2", name:"q1" %>ひとりごと</label></div>
          <div class="target col-md-5 col-sm-3 border border-success rounded-pill m-2 bg-color q1"><label><%= f.radio_button :q1, "q1_3", name:"q1" %>beautiful glider</label></div>

      
        <div class="question">
          Q2.ガッキー好きですか？
        </div>
          <div class="target col-md-5 col-sm-3 border border-success rounded-pill m-2 bg-color q2"><label><%= f.radio_button :q2, "q2_1", name:"q2" %>大好き</label></div>
          <div class="target col-md-5 col-sm-3 border border-success rounded-pill m-2 bg-color q2"><label><%= f.radio_button :q2, "q2_2", name:"q2" %>普通</label></div>
          <div class="target col-md-5 col-sm-3 border border-success rounded-pill m-2 bg-color q2"><label><%= f.radio_button :q2, "q2_3", name:"q2" %>そうでもない</label></div>
          
        <div class="question">
          Q3.昨日の晩ご飯
        </div>
          <div class="target col-md-5 col-sm-3 border border-success rounded-pill m-2 bg-color q3"><label><%= f.radio_button :q2, "q3_1", name:"q3" %>和食</label></div>
          <div class="target col-md-5 col-sm-3 border border-success rounded-pill m-2 bg-color q3"><label><%= f.radio_button :q2, "q3_2", name:"q3" %>洋食</label></div>
          <div class="target col-md-5 col-sm-3 border border-success rounded-pill m-2 bg-color q3"><label><%= f.radio_button :q2, "q3_3", name:"q3" %>中華</label></div>
        <%= f.submit '送信' %>

      <% end %>


    </div>
  </div>
</div>

